Extracted title: {{ $json.videoTitle }}
Mime type: {{ $json.mimeType }}

Instructions:
- Use the extracted title to understand what the clip shows (e.g. a movement, class, or coaching moment)
- Start each caption with a short, natural reference to what's happening in the clip
- After that opening line, add one short, warm, coaching-style sentence
- Keep each caption short and genuine, not hype-driven
- Keep wording fresh and not repetitive
- Avoid reusing these recent Instagram hashtags if possible: {{ $json.recentInstagramHashtags || "" }}
- Avoid reusing these recent TikTok hashtags if possible: {{ $json.recentTikTokHashtags || "" }}
- Avoid reusing these recent X hashtags if possible: {{ $json.recentTwitterHashtags || "" }}
